8) Hue v2 Endpunkte (Kurz-Referenz)

Listen:
    GET /clip/v2/resource/light
    GET /clip/v2/resource/room
    GET /clip/v2/resource/zone
    GET /clip/v2/resource/grouped_light

Steuern:
    Gruppe: PUT /clip/v2/resource/grouped_light/{id}

        {"on":{"on":true}}
        {"dimming":{"brightness": 35.0}}
        {"color_temperature":{"mirek": 250}}
        {"color":{"xy":{"x":0.35,"y":0.35}}}

Einzellampe: PUT /clip/v2/resource/light/{id} (gleiches Schema)

